00:00:11.434 --> 00:00:15.968 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Chanting ]

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:19.901 position:16% line:89% align:start
O Maiden of purest white,

00:00:19.934 --> 00:00:21.801 position:16% line:89% align:start
which will thou choose --

00:00:21.834 --> 00:00:25.734 position:35% line:83% align:start
Blue water
or a storm cloud?

00:00:25.767 --> 00:00:29.734 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:00:29.767 --> 00:00:31.767 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:00:35.968 --> 00:00:38.367 position:30% line:77% align:start
[ Bed creaks ]
[ Grunts ]

00:00:40.734 --> 00:00:43.968 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Yawns ]

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.400 position:47% line:83% align:start
Alright, Fena.
Let's go...

00:00:46.434 --> 00:00:49.267 position:35% line:89% align:start
Uh...sure!

00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:51.400 position:19% line:5% align:start
[ Singing in Japanese ]

00:00:51.434 --> 00:01:00.734 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:00.767 --> 00:01:10.267 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:10.300 --> 00:01:19.601 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:19.634 --> 00:01:28.934 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:28.968 --> 00:01:38.467 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:38.501 --> 00:01:47.801 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:47.834 --> 00:01:57.334 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:57.367 --> 00:02:06.667 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:06.701 --> 00:02:16.000 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:16.033 --> 00:02:25.133 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:25.167 --> 00:02:29.667 position:38% line:77% align:start
Tsubaki:
Ah, and you two are absolutely
 <i>sure</i> this is the destination?

00:02:29.701 --> 00:02:30.901 position:47% line:83% align:start
Yeah of course
we're sure!

00:02:30.934 --> 00:02:32.701 position:58% line:83% align:start
He said
Debar Hopenstein!

00:02:32.734 --> 00:02:34.834 position:5% line:89% align:start
And at Dresnadeen too!

00:02:34.868 --> 00:02:36.234 position:21% line:83% align:start
Wasn't it
Dres-neen-a-steen?

00:02:36.267 --> 00:02:39.100 position:47% line:83% align:start
Not even close!
It's Dresnen-bar-diddlepot.

00:02:39.133 --> 00:02:40.501 position:5% line:89% align:start
Ahh yeah, that's it!

00:02:40.534 --> 00:02:44.300 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ Sighs ] Why'd I bother?
I'll just ask Fena later.

00:02:44.334 --> 00:02:45.534 position:16% line:89% align:start
Huh?Huh?

00:02:45.567 --> 00:02:47.467 position:16% line:89% align:start
Why?Why?

00:02:47.501 --> 00:02:50.000 position:27% line:89% align:start
Libar Oberstein.

00:02:50.033 --> 00:02:52.200 position:47% line:83% align:start
Hmm, they must
mean Dresden.

00:02:52.234 --> 00:02:54.701 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yeah, I knew they had no idea
what they were talking about.

00:02:54.734 --> 00:02:56.734 position:30% line:83% align:start
But roger that.
Thanks.

00:02:58.234 --> 00:03:02.133 position:24% line:71% align:start
[ Material tightens ]
Okay,
that should do it.

00:03:02.167 --> 00:03:04.200 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'll change it
again tomorrow.

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:11.267 position:24% line:89% align:start
Umm...

00:03:11.300 --> 00:03:14.133 position:50% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry...
for being so impulsive.

00:03:14.167 --> 00:03:16.400 position:13% line:83% align:start
There's no need
to keep apologizing.

00:03:16.434 --> 00:03:18.267 position:7% line:83% align:start
You made your point
the first time.

00:03:18.300 --> 00:03:20.200 position:50% line:89% align:start
It's just...

00:03:20.234 --> 00:03:22.400 position:35% line:83% align:start
Protecting
you's our job.

00:03:22.434 --> 00:03:23.701 position:33% line:89% align:start
So it's fine.

00:03:23.734 --> 00:03:26.067 position:16% line:83% align:start
That may be,
but from now on...

00:03:26.100 --> 00:03:29.167 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna work hard to try and
be more useful to the team.

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:31.167 position:33% line:83% align:start
That won't be
necessary.

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:32.868 position:38% line:83% align:start
Besides,
you're sorely mistaken

00:03:32.901 --> 00:03:35.167 position:30% line:83% align:start
if you presume
you can be helpful to us.

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:36.767 position:21% line:83% align:start
Stop putting yourself
at risk.

00:03:36.801 --> 00:03:38.434 position:24% line:89% align:start
Do not do it again!

00:03:38.467 --> 00:03:39.567 position:5% line:89% align:start
Don't order me around!

00:03:39.601 --> 00:03:41.601 position:13% line:83% align:start
Like it or not,
I will contribute something.

00:03:41.634 --> 00:03:44.467 position:10% line:83% align:start
That attitude of yours is what
keeps getting us into trouble!

00:03:44.501 --> 00:03:46.834 position:21% line:83% align:start
Go pick fleas off your dog
and stay out of the way!

00:03:46.868 --> 00:03:48.367 position:24% line:89% align:start
Never!

00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:50.334 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ Both growl ]

00:03:50.367 --> 00:03:52.601 position:33% line:89% align:start
"Now, now..."

00:04:00.100 --> 00:04:01.434 position:35% line:89% align:start
What is it?

00:04:01.467 --> 00:04:03.033 position:44% line:83% align:start
It's not like you
to raise your voice

00:04:03.067 --> 00:04:05.100 position:50% line:83% align:start
when someone
gets under your skin.

00:04:05.133 --> 00:04:06.834 position:38% line:83% align:start
Normally, you'd just
whack people on the head

00:04:06.868 --> 00:04:08.601 position:38% line:89% align:start
and be done with it.

00:04:10.868 --> 00:04:12.601 position:10% line:89% align:start
Just let me pass.

00:04:39.767 --> 00:04:43.334 position:55% line:83% align:start
Shitan: Fena.
[ Gasps ]

00:04:43.367 --> 00:04:45.234 position:24% line:89% align:start
Shitan?

00:04:45.267 --> 00:04:49.100 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Peaceful music plays ]

00:04:49.133 --> 00:04:51.033 position:44% line:83% align:start
We could hear you
through the whole ship.

00:04:51.067 --> 00:04:53.234 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:04:53.267 --> 00:04:55.234 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't let
Yukimaru get to you.

00:04:55.267 --> 00:04:57.200 position:10% line:89% align:start
He's like that with everyone.

00:05:00.100 --> 00:05:02.267 position:55% line:83% align:start
Hey, Shitan...
Yeah?

00:05:02.300 --> 00:05:05.200 position:16% line:83% align:start
I would like you to teach me
how to use a weapon.

00:05:05.234 --> 00:05:07.501 position:27% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:05:07.534 --> 00:05:09.667 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Twang! ]

00:05:15.734 --> 00:05:17.334 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why isn't it going far?

00:05:17.367 --> 00:05:19.367 position:7% line:83% align:start
This'll take longer
than I thought.

00:05:19.400 --> 00:05:20.701 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:05:20.734 --> 00:05:22.634 position:5% line:77% align:start
I have a brilliant idea.
Huh?

00:05:24.067 --> 00:05:26.701 position:47% line:83% align:start
No!
No way!

00:05:26.734 --> 00:05:28.133 position:47% line:83% align:start
Can't you help
a girl out?

00:05:28.167 --> 00:05:30.200 position:38% line:83% align:start
After all, you and I
are friends, right?

00:05:30.234 --> 00:05:32.067 position:10% line:83% align:start
I don't recall us
being that close.

00:05:32.100 --> 00:05:33.400 position:64% line:83% align:start
Ugh?!
Besides!

00:05:33.434 --> 00:05:35.133 position:10% line:83% align:start
I don't like what
that jerk's implying with

00:05:35.167 --> 00:05:37.267 position:16% line:83% align:start
"Oh, if Fena
can't handle a bow...

00:05:37.300 --> 00:05:41.133 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then give her an easy,
girly weapon like a gun!"

00:05:41.167 --> 00:05:43.000 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well he knows
how to run away!

00:05:43.033 --> 00:05:45.501 position:5% line:83% align:start
Let's get one thing straight
here. You listening?

00:05:45.534 --> 00:05:47.934 position:10% line:77% align:start
Guns aren't toys
and aren't something you
can master in a day!

00:05:47.968 --> 00:05:49.367 position:7% line:83% align:start
Their construction
and design,

00:05:49.400 --> 00:05:51.400 position:5% line:83% align:start
gunpowder, their features,
and their history!

00:05:51.434 --> 00:05:54.000 position:5% line:83% align:start
Before you can train
with a gun you study those.

00:05:54.033 --> 00:05:55.334 position:16% line:83% align:start
Actually no,
first I want you

00:05:55.367 --> 00:05:56.834 position:13% line:83% align:start
to take a look
at this thing I just invented.

00:05:56.868 --> 00:05:59.567 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's based on the same principle
as a bean planting machine

00:05:59.601 --> 00:06:01.901 position:5% line:83% align:start
using the power of spin
and gravity to--

00:06:01.934 --> 00:06:03.801 position:19% line:83% align:start
Huh? Fena?
Where'd you go? Fena?!

00:06:03.834 --> 00:06:08.067 position:69% line:77% align:start
Shitan...
She supplies me
with endless amusement.

00:06:14.467 --> 00:06:16.133 position:13% line:89% align:start
Fena: Tsubaki!

00:06:18.868 --> 00:06:20.133 position:38% line:89% align:start
Wait, you want me...

00:06:20.167 --> 00:06:21.601 position:27% line:89% align:start
to teach sword fighting?

00:06:21.634 --> 00:06:24.133 position:58% line:83% align:start
To you?
For what?

00:06:24.167 --> 00:06:25.968 position:5% line:83% align:start
Shitan said that out
of everyone on-board,

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:27.467 position:5% line:83% align:start
you're the person closest
to my skill level

00:06:27.501 --> 00:06:29.734 position:5% line:83% align:start
so it might be easier
to learn from you.

00:06:29.767 --> 00:06:31.701 position:61% line:83% align:start
Ahhh.
That makes sense!

00:06:31.734 --> 00:06:33.400 position:58% line:83% align:start
Okay so
what you're saying is...

00:06:33.434 --> 00:06:35.634 position:7% line:83% align:start
In comparison to everyone else,
I'm the worst swordsman here.

00:06:35.667 --> 00:06:38.234 position:30% line:83% align:start
So I'm the ideal person
to teach a total newbie.

00:06:38.267 --> 00:06:39.701 position:27% line:89% align:start
I see right through him.

00:06:39.734 --> 00:06:41.868 position:10% line:89% align:start
He thought he was so clever...

00:06:41.901 --> 00:06:43.767 position:58% line:89% align:start
Shitan!

00:06:43.801 --> 00:06:46.567 position:27% line:83% align:start
Tsubaki, is this
that broth stuff?

00:06:46.601 --> 00:06:49.334 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's too bland and boring
for my refined palate.

00:06:49.367 --> 00:06:52.300 position:16% line:83% align:start
Can I at least add a head
of bonito or something?

00:06:52.334 --> 00:06:54.634 position:55% line:89% align:start
Get out!

00:06:54.667 --> 00:06:56.667 position:27% line:77% align:start
[ Buzzer sounds ]
Mnh-mnh.

00:06:56.701 --> 00:06:58.033 position:33% line:77% align:start
No way!
No way!

00:06:58.067 --> 00:07:01.300 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:01.334 --> 00:07:05.334 position:16% line:83% align:start
In the end...
everybody turned me down.

00:07:05.367 --> 00:07:07.767 position:10% line:83% align:start
Could I really be
that hopeless?

00:07:13.467 --> 00:07:14.868 position:47% line:89% align:start
I'll teach you.

00:07:14.901 --> 00:07:17.667 position:19% line:83% align:start
With the caveat that swords
aren't exactly my strong suit.

00:07:17.701 --> 00:07:19.200 position:5% line:89% align:start
You'd do that for me?

00:07:19.234 --> 00:07:21.901 position:5% line:83% align:start
And I took you for the type
that was good at everything!

00:07:21.934 --> 00:07:23.801 position:61% line:83% align:start
[ Chuckles ]
Hardly.

00:07:23.834 --> 00:07:25.100 position:38% line:83% align:start
I'd say I'm probably
the worst swordsman

00:07:25.133 --> 00:07:27.434 position:47% line:83% align:start
out of everyone
on this ship, by far.

00:07:27.467 --> 00:07:29.367 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're just
being humble, right?

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:31.868 position:41% line:83% align:start
No, I'm telling you
the truth...

00:07:31.901 --> 00:07:33.267 position:69% line:83% align:start
And while
we're being honest...

00:07:33.300 --> 00:07:35.467 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's because I was always
around someone...

00:07:35.501 --> 00:07:37.501 position:44% line:83% align:start
who made me feel
I'd never measure up.

00:07:37.534 --> 00:07:39.734 position:44% line:83% align:start
It didn't matter
how hard I tried.

00:07:42.834 --> 00:07:46.801 position:21% line:83% align:start
Not wanting to be shown up
by the guy, I grew reckless,

00:07:46.834 --> 00:07:48.367 position:38% line:83% align:start
and would charge out
ahead of him.

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:53.334 position:7% line:83% align:start
But as a result, he had to save
my life again and again.

00:07:53.367 --> 00:07:58.133 position:5% line:83% align:start
It got to a point, where I swore
I'd save his life next time.

00:07:58.167 --> 00:07:59.701 position:19% line:89% align:start
Not by running out ahead...

00:07:59.734 --> 00:08:01.834 position:44% line:89% align:start
but from behind.

00:08:01.868 --> 00:08:04.067 position:24% line:83% align:start
So that's why you took up
the bow.

00:08:04.100 --> 00:08:06.267 position:13% line:83% align:start
Let's head in.
It's cold out.

00:08:06.300 --> 00:08:09.334 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:09.367 --> 00:08:11.100 position:58% line:89% align:start
Shitan!

00:08:14.267 --> 00:08:15.634 position:30% line:89% align:start
I have to get stronger.

00:08:15.667 --> 00:08:18.834 position:5% line:83% align:start
I want to be able to protect him
for a change.

00:08:18.868 --> 00:08:20.567 position:44% line:89% align:start
The way you did.

00:08:23.901 --> 00:08:25.434 position:10% line:83% align:start
Then we'll begin
tomorrow.

00:08:25.467 --> 00:08:27.200 position:10% line:89% align:start
Before breakfast.

00:08:42.467 --> 00:08:44.734 position:41% line:83% align:start
 <i>I want to be able</i>
 <i>to protect him...</i>

00:08:51.667 --> 00:08:53.734 position:5% line:89% align:start
Have you seen Shitan?

00:08:53.767 --> 00:08:55.067 position:61% line:83% align:start
Uh...
Why?

00:08:55.100 --> 00:08:56.767 position:10% line:83% align:start
He's the only one
with the screws for this.

00:08:56.801 --> 00:08:58.467 position:5% line:77% align:start
So I need to find him.
Oh!

00:08:58.501 --> 00:09:00.434 position:50% line:77% align:start
Well uh, look --
About this morning...

00:09:00.467 --> 00:09:02.834 position:33% line:83% align:start
Shitan was on the deck
a few minutes ago!

00:09:02.868 --> 00:09:04.067 position:44% line:83% align:start
Up there with me,
actually.

00:09:04.100 --> 00:09:05.701 position:52% line:83% align:start
He might be
in his cabin now.

00:09:05.734 --> 00:09:08.367 position:5% line:83% align:start
Between us, I think I'm starting
to understand his sex appeal!

00:09:08.400 --> 00:09:09.868 position:41% line:83% align:start
He's got such a way
with women.

00:09:09.901 --> 00:09:11.434 position:47% line:83% align:start
He's handsome,
strong, and kind.

00:09:11.467 --> 00:09:12.767 position:41% line:89% align:start
It's almost unfair.

00:09:12.801 --> 00:09:15.601 position:55% line:83% align:start
Gah! Not
that I noticed!

00:09:15.634 --> 00:09:17.367 position:44% line:89% align:start
Well, good night!

00:09:21.767 --> 00:09:23.501 position:27% line:89% align:start
Way with women...

00:09:28.901 --> 00:09:31.767 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:31.801 --> 00:09:33.701 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:09:33.734 --> 00:09:35.567 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Grunts ]

00:09:35.601 --> 00:09:38.367 position:72% line:83% align:start
Hah!
[ Yawns ]

00:09:38.400 --> 00:09:40.934 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ Yells, grunts ]

00:09:40.968 --> 00:09:42.834 position:41% line:89% align:start
Again!

00:09:42.868 --> 00:09:44.534 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:44.567 --> 00:09:45.934 position:61% line:89% align:start
Hah!

00:09:45.968 --> 00:09:49.000 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Shouting quickly ]

00:09:49.033 --> 00:09:52.467 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Panting ]

00:09:52.501 --> 00:09:53.834 position:58% line:89% align:start
Again!

00:09:53.868 --> 00:09:55.400 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Gasping ]

00:09:55.434 --> 00:09:57.434 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:57.467 --> 00:09:59.067 position:35% line:83% align:start
Okay, Fena.
If there's one thing

00:09:59.100 --> 00:10:00.567 position:35% line:83% align:start
I can teach
you as the worst swordsman here,

00:10:00.601 --> 00:10:03.434 position:33% line:83% align:start
it's this --
draw it, and stab the other guy.

00:10:03.467 --> 00:10:05.100 position:55% line:83% align:start
Draw it,
and stab the other guy.

00:10:05.133 --> 00:10:06.767 position:44% line:83% align:start
Yep!
Stab.

00:10:06.801 --> 00:10:12.868 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:12.901 --> 00:10:15.868 position:61% line:83% align:start
Ahh!
Ha! Huh!

00:10:15.901 --> 00:10:21.467 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:21.501 --> 00:10:22.901 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:10:22.934 --> 00:10:24.834 position:58% line:83% align:start
You're late!
Yah!

00:10:24.868 --> 00:10:26.868 position:44% line:83% align:start
All wrong! Focus!
Elbows in!

00:10:26.901 --> 00:10:28.167 position:41% line:83% align:start
Your right elbow's
dropping!

00:10:28.200 --> 00:10:30.067 position:41% line:83% align:start
What'd I just say?
Really?

00:10:30.100 --> 00:10:31.434 position:47% line:83% align:start
Now your back's
all wrong too!

00:10:31.467 --> 00:10:33.501 position:5% line:83% align:start
I swear, if you don't pick up
those elbows...

00:10:33.534 --> 00:10:35.601 position:5% line:83% align:start
See, you want them up like this,
cause if not you're--

00:10:35.634 --> 00:10:36.901 position:35% line:83% align:start
[ Kaboom! ]
Aah!

00:10:36.934 --> 00:10:38.868 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Growls ]

00:10:38.901 --> 00:10:40.234 position:16% line:83% align:start
Shoot before
my go-ahead again,

00:10:40.267 --> 00:10:42.000 position:5% line:83% align:start
and that's the last gun
you'll lay hands on!

00:10:42.033 --> 00:10:43.300 position:5% line:77% align:start
Is that clear?
Fena: Yes, ma'am.

00:10:43.334 --> 00:10:44.901 position:5% line:77% align:start
I can't hear you!
Yes, ma'am!

00:10:44.934 --> 00:10:46.100 position:35% line:83% align:start
Karin: Look, the meek
may inherit the earth,

00:10:46.133 --> 00:10:47.534 position:50% line:83% align:start
but they make
crappy marksmen!

00:10:47.567 --> 00:10:50.133 position:13% line:83% align:start
Ya can't shoot, cause the gun
doesn't respect you!

00:10:50.801 --> 00:10:53.167 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Groans, whimpers ]

00:10:54.400 --> 00:10:55.400 position:27% line:89% align:start
That was brutal.

