00:12:04.934 --> 00:12:06.901 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:06.934 --> 00:12:08.734 position:72% line:83% align:start
Oh.
Ooh.

00:12:08.767 --> 00:12:10.767 position:27% line:89% align:start
Whoa.

00:12:10.801 --> 00:12:12.567 position:47% line:89% align:start
Mm?

