00:12:26.501 --> 00:12:33.434 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:33.467 --> 00:12:37.968 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:40.767 position:35% line:89% align:start
Well, well.

00:12:40.801 --> 00:12:41.968 position:41% line:89% align:start
