00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:43.334 position:21% line:89% align:start
I...uh...

00:12:43.367 --> 00:12:46.200 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's a relic,
passed down by my people.

00:12:46.234 --> 00:12:49.868 position:16% line:83% align:start
Circumstances now dictate
we learn its origins.

00:12:49.901 --> 00:12:52.634 position:19% line:83% align:start
No information would be
too trivial.

00:12:52.667 --> 00:12:54.367 position:21% line:89% align:start
