meet you, miss.

00:13:15.534 --> 00:13:17.501 position:44% line:83% align:start
Uh...
I'm Fena.

00:13:17.534 --> 00:13:18.634 position:16% line:89% align:start
For starters.

00:13:18.667 --> 00:13:20.167 position:5% line:83% align:start
