[ Gasps ]
That'd be great!

00:13:24.934 --> 00:13:27.300 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you!

00:13:27.334 --> 00:13:29.234 position:5% line:83% align:start
All exports from this village
are submitted

00:13:29.267 --> 00:13:31.701 position:5% line:83% align:start
to the Burgermeister
for inspection.

00:13:31.734 --> 00:13:35.701 position:7% line:83% align:start
