00:13:37.000 --> 00:13:38.734 position:44% line:89% align:start
That is our way.

00:13:38.767 --> 00:13:40.300 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's odd.

00:13:40.334 --> 00:13:43.367 position:55% line:89% align:start
