You're trained?

00:13:59.400 --> 00:14:01.767 position:44% line:77% align:start
[ Gasps ]
Contact!
Oh, my...

00:14:01.801 --> 00:14:03.100 position:38% line:89% align:start
I wouldn't say that.

00:14:03.133 --> 00:14:04.734 position:41% line:83% align:start
I just picked it up
as I went along.

00:14:04.767 --> 00:14:07.133 position:13% line:83% align:start
Self-taught is
the best way to learn.

00:14:07.167 --> 00:14:09.434 position:27% line:71% align:start
[ Grunts ]
Ooh it's
a two-part touch!

00:14:09.467 --> 00:14:12.300 position:5% line:83% align:start
Looks like she's got
wandering hands.

00:14:12.334 --> 00:14:14.834 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're reading too much into it,
you ants!

00:14:14.868 --> 00:14:16.601 position:21% line:83% align:start
They don't meet many women
like her.

00:14:16.634 --> 00:14:18.234 position:27% line:89% align:start
Let them have their fun.

00:14:18.267 --> 00:14:20.467 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's just past
that turn there.

00:14:20.501 --> 00:14:23.968 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:26.067 position:10% line:89% align:start
Okay, this is it.

00:14:33.667 --> 00:14:36.367 position:33% line:83% align:start
We're here...
the Burgermeister's office.

00:14:38.567 --> 00:14:39.834 position:21% line:89% align:start
Please wait outside.

00:14:39.868 --> 00:14:41.734 position:27% line:83% align:start
He's known to be
a bit difficult.

