What?
What do you mean?

00:14:47.934 --> 00:14:49.434 position:52% line:83% align:start
She clearly
fancies you.

00:14:49.467 --> 00:14:51.267 position:50% line:83% align:start
If you tried,
you could go all the way.

00:14:51.300 --> 00:14:52.834 position:27% line:83% align:start
Huh?
Go where with her?

00:14:52.868 --> 00:14:55.067 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:14:55.100 --> 00:14:58.334 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's okay! He'll allow
