♪♪

00:15:40.968 --> 00:15:50.300 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:15:50.334 --> 00:15:51.834 position:55% line:83% align:start
If we all
stay the night...

00:15:51.868 --> 00:15:54.501 position:16% line:83% align:start
you know that woman is gonna
sneak into Yukimaru's bed.

00:15:54.534 --> 00:15:57.434 position:5% line:83% align:start
[ Gasps ] Wh-why would you
think that?

00:15:57.467 --> 00:16:00.834 position:38% line:89% align:start
Years of experience.

00:16:00.868 --> 00:16:03.000 position:5% line:89% align:start
How does this look to you?

00:16:03.033 --> 00:16:04.200 position:44% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ] Danke!

00:16:04.234 --> 00:16:05.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
Grandpa,
he's finished!

00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:11.067 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:16:11.100 --> 00:16:14.434 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ Germanic accent ]
This is impressive work.

00:16:14.467 --> 00:16:15.667 position:47% line:89% align:start
Do you like it?

00:16:15.701 --> 00:16:18.634 position:27% line:89% align:start
Very much indeed.

00:16:18.667 --> 00:16:21.901 position:13% line:83% align:start
This knife was given to me
by my father as a gift

00:16:21.934 --> 00:16:24.033 position:19% line:89% align:start
when I was just a boy.

00:16:24.067 --> 00:16:25.434 position:33% line:89% align:start
I wanted it.

00:16:25.467 --> 00:16:28.367 position:24% line:89% align:start
So I pestered him.

00:16:28.400 --> 00:16:30.901 position:5% line:83% align:start
It looks as new as the day
it was handed to me.

00:16:30.934 --> 00:16:34.167 position:13% line:83% align:start
It brings back
such memories.

00:16:36.400 --> 00:16:38.767 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'd love to
return the favor.

00:16:38.801 --> 00:16:45.734 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:16:45.767 --> 00:16:47.334 position:24% line:83% align:start
Kaede:
I'm so bored...

00:16:47.367 --> 00:16:50.100 position:61% line:77% align:start
Enju:
Tell me about it, we haven't
had scenes in forever.

00:16:50.133 --> 00:16:53.367 position:5% line:83% align:start
Makaba, I'd try to get
a line in if I were you.

00:16:53.400 --> 00:16:55.300 position:24% line:83% align:start
Makaba: [ Muffled ]
This is delicious!

00:16:57.434 --> 00:16:58.701 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now then...

00:16:58.734 --> 00:16:59.934 position:19% line:89% align:start
The stone.

00:16:59.968 --> 00:17:02.801 position:5% line:83% align:start
You wish to know its origins,
right?

00:17:02.834 --> 00:17:04.100 position:41% line:89% align:start
Please.

00:17:04.133 --> 00:17:06.434 position:5% line:83% align:start
