was indeed manufactured

00:17:06.467 --> 00:17:07.834 position:10% line:89% align:start
in this village.

00:17:07.868 --> 00:17:09.200 position:21% line:89% align:start
Th-that's incredible!

00:17:09.234 --> 00:17:11.734 position:47% line:83% align:start
What d'ya know?
You were right!

00:17:11.767 --> 00:17:13.267 position:27% line:89% align:start
Do you know when?

00:17:13.300 --> 00:17:15.434 position:19% line:83% align:start
And where it was made,
and what it could used be for?

00:17:15.467 --> 00:17:18.200 position:5% line:83% align:start
Luckily, before any of our
products are shipped out...

00:17:18.234 --> 00:17:21.634 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's inscribed in a way that's
invisible to the naked eye...

00:17:21.667 --> 00:17:25.501 position:5% line:83% align:start
To record its production date
and who commissioned it.

00:17:25.534 --> 00:17:30.834 position:5% line:83% align:start
And this item has "D3756"
etched into it.

00:17:30.868 --> 00:17:33.534 position:16% line:83% align:start
Arya.
Ja?

00:17:33.567 --> 00:17:34.968 position:5% line:89% align:start
On the shelf over there...

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:37.033 position:10% line:83% align:start
Can you fetch me
that blue book?

00:17:57.501 --> 00:18:00.234 position:21% line:89% align:start
This is most unusual.

00:18:00.267 --> 00:18:03.167 position:13% line:83% align:start
The stone <i>didn't</i> originate
from this village.

00:18:03.200 --> 00:18:05.734 position:21% line:83% align:start
The client brought it
to have it carved here.

00:18:05.767 --> 00:18:07.033 position:21% line:89% align:start
It came from France.

00:18:07.067 --> 00:18:10.033 position:5% line:89% align:start
The year of production was 1436.

00:18:10.067 --> 00:18:12.634 position:7% line:83% align:start
