some sort of joke?

00:18:15.868 --> 00:18:17.767 position:61% line:83% align:start
What?
What does it say?

00:18:17.801 --> 00:18:19.767 position:27% line:83% align:start
What's the matter
is something wrong?

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:28.701 position:44% line:83% align:start
Arya:
La Pucelle d'Orléans.

00:18:28.734 --> 00:18:31.234 position:13% line:89% align:start
Wait, La pucelle d'Orleans?

00:18:31.267 --> 00:18:33.467 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hang on, does this mean...

00:18:33.501 --> 00:18:36.667 position:13% line:83% align:start
