00:18:36.701 --> 00:18:37.868 position:27% line:89% align:start
Jeanne of Arc...

00:18:37.901 --> 00:18:39.400 position:41% line:77% align:start
Wait, what?
Look at the signature.

00:18:39.434 --> 00:18:41.534 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's hard to make out,
but it says "Jeanne."

00:18:41.567 --> 00:18:44.167 position:47% line:83% align:start
If that's true,
that would be amazing, right?

00:18:44.200 --> 00:18:46.467 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well, in all likelihood
it's just a prank.

00:18:46.501 --> 00:18:48.968 position:10% line:77% align:start
But this is not our concern.
All: [ Gasp ]

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:51.567 position:10% line:83% align:start
Joan of Arc being the client
is irrelevant?

00:18:51.601 --> 00:18:53.100 position:13% line:89% align:start
Is that what you're saying?

00:18:53.133 --> 00:18:55.567 position:19% line:83% align:start
The fame and status of
any of our clients

00:18:55.601 --> 00:18:57.100 position:21% line:89% align:start
is never our concern.

00:18:57.133 --> 00:18:59.167 position:21% line:83% align:start
