00:21:15.133 --> 00:21:17.467 position:10% line:83% align:start
That French word,
"la Pucelle."

00:21:17.501 --> 00:21:20.067 position:61% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:21:20.100 --> 00:21:23.267 position:10% line:83% align:start
Like maybe I used
to call someone that?

00:21:23.300 --> 00:21:26.267 position:5% line:83% align:start
Or maybe someone I knew
used to call me that.

00:21:26.300 --> 00:21:33.834 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:21:33.868 --> 00:21:41.567 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:21:41.601 --> 00:21:44.300 position:44% line:83% align:start
Abel:
La Pucelle...

00:21:44.334 --> 00:21:53.634 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:21:53.667 --> 00:21:55.234 position:35% line:89% align:start
What is it?

00:21:55.267 --> 00:21:58.234 position:41% line:83% align:start
I've received word
